Package: CPLogit
Type: Package
Title: Borrowing between regression coefficients using prior information on clustering
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-06-30
Author: Sally Paganin 
Maintainer: Sally Paganin <sally.paganin@berkeley.edu>
Description: The CPLogit package provide functions to estimate Bayesian linear and logistic models using the Centered Partition (CP) process prior described in the paper Centered Partition Processes: Informative Priors for Clustering. 
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.0),
Depends:
    mvtnorm (>= 0.9)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
